title: Philosophy 4: A Story of Harvard University
creator: Owen Wister
description: LibriVox recording of Philosophy 4: A Story of Harvard University, by Owen Wister. Read by David Wales. Owen Wister's wry humor enlivens this comedic story of three sophomores during exam week at Harvard. (Summary by David Wales) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
